Cost effectiveness of modified fractionation radiotherapy versus conventional 
radiotherapy for unresected non-small-cell lung cancer patients.

Ramaekers BL(1), Joore MA, Lueza B, Bonastre J, Mauguen A, Pignon JP, Le Pechoux 
C, De Ruysscher DK; MAR-LC Collaborative group; Grutters JP.

Collaborators: Arriagada R, Bae K, Ball D, Baumann M, Behrendt K, Belani CP, 
Beresford J, Bishop J, Bonner JA, Choy H, Dahlberg SE, De Ruysscher D, Dische S, 
