hyperactivity risk in 33%.
CONCLUSION: A high percentage of adolescents show difficulties in several areas 
(disease knowledge, peer relationship, school failure...) that can have an 
impact on their adult lives. Further studies are needed to evaluate their origin 
and development in depth, as well as interventions to modify this situation.

