Economic evaluation of brief psychodynamic interpersonal therapy in patients 
with multisomatoform disorder.

Chernyak N(1), Sattel H(2), Scheer M(3), Baechle C(3), Kruse J(4), Henningsen 
P(2), Icks A(1).
